items.description: A long-sleeve button-up shirt in an olive green color. It has a classic collar and appears to be made from a lightweight, slightly crinkled fabric.
A colorful plaid button-up shirt with a collar and chest pockets.
A pair of gradient jeans with a black upper half that transitions into a light gray or white towards the bottom.
A casual, long-sleeve hoodie made of soft fabric, featuring a front zipper and two pockets. The inside of the hood has a contrasting light blue lining.
Navy blue pajama pants with a football motif pattern, featuring an elastic waistband and loose fit suitable for casual wear.
A blue and white striped long-sleeve shirt with a V-neck opening and a relaxed collar.
A short-sleeve button-up shirt with a collar, featuring an abstract animal pattern.
A sleeveless quilted vest with a front zipper and a subtle geometric pattern. It features a ribbed collar and small logo detail on the left side.
A floral patterned dress with short sleeves and a flowy silhouette, featuring a black background with colorful flower prints.
A striped long-sleeve shirt with alternating navy blue and white horizontal stripes. Features yellow trim on the neckline and cuffs.
Long-sleeve button-up shirt with a plaid pattern and a structured collar.
This is a short-sleeve, purple t-shirt with a round neckline.
A short-sleeve green shirt with white horizontal stripes and small scattered ice cream cone motifs.
A navy blue midi skirt with small white polka dots and thin straps.
A gray short-sleeve T-shirt with a graphic print featuring a speech bubble with the text 'WHAT'S UP?' and a small cartoon character.
A knitted beanie with a white top and a wide band, featuring Russian text and design elements in blue, white, and red.
A long, tiered dress with a button-up top and three-quarter sleeves.
A short-sleeved, color-blocked t-shirt with the 'FILA' logo across the chest. The top section is red, the middle is white, and the bottom is navy blue.
A short-sleeved, quilted puffer jacket in a light pink color with a V-neckline.
A short-sleeved, navy blue polo shirt with a collar and a three-button placket.
A long-sleeve button-up shirt with a collar, made from a fabric that appears slightly textured.
A pair of dark grey distressed jeans with rips at the knees and a fitted design.
Sleeveless top with a patterned design.
Casual beige shorts with an elastic waistband, suitable for relaxed settings.
A dark-colored short-sleeve athletic shirt with branding and graphics on the front.
This is a short-sleeve color-block shirt featuring three horizontal panels in different shades.
A black and white striped short-sleeve dress, knee-length with a fitted silhouette.
A navy blue t-shirt with a logo and geometric shapes printed in white, pink, and teal.
White sandals with a flat sole. They feature multiple straps, including an ankle strap with a buckle for fastening. There is a subtle decorative buckle on top.
Khaki pants with a classic design, featuring rolled-up cuffs.
A pair of dark navy blue pants with an elastic waistband and a simple, straight cut.
A long-sleeved checkered shirt with a button-up front and a collar.
A short-sleeved shirt with a zipper neckline and contrasting trim on the collar and sleeves.
A long, open-front ribbed cardigan with full sleeves and a relaxed fit.
A pair of gray denim jeans with a button and zipper closure, featuring front and back pockets.
A short-sleeve button-up shirt with a subtle pattern and standard collar.
A black jacket with a high collar and two silver zipper pockets. It has a fur trim around the collar, cuffs, and hem. The main zipper is diagonal.
A basic solid black T-shirt with short sleeves and a crew neckline.
A cropped, knitted sweater with cable knit detailing on the front and ribbed hems.
White flat sandals with strappy design and gold buckle detail, featuring an open toe and ankle strap.
